16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 17-113, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 17-113. A. In determining annual increments for teacher
20 salaries and in computing Foundation Aid, time spent in military
21 service during a period of national emergency shall be counted, not
22 to exceed five (5) years prior to the current year. No more than
23 five (5) years of such military service shall be used in determining
24 eligibility or benefits under the Teachers' Retirement System.
